obj_root_law:
  slug the-cigarettes-and-other-tobacco-products-prohibition-of-advertisement-and-regulation-of-trade-and-commerce-production-supply-and-distribution-act-2003
  handle (2053)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Cigarettes and Other Tobacco Products (Prohibition of Advertisement and Regulation of Trade and Commerce, Production, Supply and Distribution) Act, 2003`
  actNumber (34)
  enactmentDate 2003-05-18
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2053`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `सिगरेट और अन्‍य तंबाकू उत्‍पाद (विज्ञापन का प्रतिषेध और व्‍यापार तथा वाणिज्‍य, उत्‍पादन, प्रदाय और वितरण का विनियमन) अधिनियम, 2003`
  actYear (2003)
  ministry `Ministry of Health and Family Welfare`
  department `Department of Health and Family Welfare`
  longTitle `An Act to prohibit the advertisement of, and to provide for the regulation of trade and commerce in, and production, supply and distribution of, cigarettes and other tobacco products and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate 01-12-2007
  notification `1st December, 2007, sub-sections (1), (2), (3) and (4) of sec. 7, ss. 8, 9, 10 and 20, vide notification No. S.O. 1955(E), dated 16th November, 2007, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec 3(ii).`
